dc_title_s: The League of Nations hand map of the world : illustrating its activities and the territorial changes since 1914
dc_description_s: George Phillips & Son. League of Nations Union. Alternate title: The League of Nations maps of the world. Multiple Mollweide projection. Ancillary maps: Europe illustrating the activities of the League of Nations and the territorial changes since 1914 (1:6,000,000), with inset maps of Iceland and Finland; African mandates (1:12,000); Asiatic mandates (1:6,000,000); Pacific mandates (1:12,000). Charts showing racial minorities in Europe, Data on world's population.Illutrated with country's flags.
